Southern Company Gas is engaged in the distribution of natural gas in four states through the natural gas distribution utilities. The
natural gas distribution utilities construct, manage, and maintain intrastate natural gas pipelines and distribution facilities. Details of
the natural gas distribution utilities at December 31, 2019 are as follows:
